    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gary Goat RPG! Legend of the Jewel Seeds (Demo)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Gary and his friends on an adventure to return the legendary Jewel Seeds to the Inner Garden!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A colorful, isometric turn-based RPG inspired by Super Mario RPG and the SNES era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a demo of a full game that is yet to be completed and will serve as an introduction to the main mechanics and story of the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Features</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 full chapter of gameplay (~first 3 hours  of the full game)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based, strategic combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.5D, isometric platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time-based attacks and a status-focused magic system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful, retro-style graphics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305340/extras/e5d6ec67426f7995b5c86f2cbc45efee.poster.avif?t=1760463058\" width=394 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305340/extras/e5d6ec67426f7995b5c86f2cbc45efee.webm?t=1760463058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305340/extras/e5d6ec67426f7995b5c86f2cbc45efee.mp4?t=1760463058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
